p356
aVBoseman.
p357
aVThe guy has talent, and it\u2019s on display.
p358
aVHe captures Brown from start to finish.
p359
aVFrom his early convictions that he could be something special to the excesses of super-stardom.
p360
aVBozeman shows us the doubts, the confidence, the flamboyance, the regrets and the talent (including some amazing dance moves) that made Brown a living legend.
p361
aVThe story doesn\u2019t give us much about Brown\u2019s political activism, although it shows him convincing the mayor of Boston that he should allow Brown\u2019s concert to go ahead shortly after the Reverend Martin Luther King, Jr.\u2019s assassination.
p362
